				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%C4%90inh-S%E1%BB%ADu-h%E1%BA%A1-ng%C5%A9-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%C3%A3n-giai-H%E1%BB%93-Trai-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-v%C3%A3ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-Tr%E1%BB%8B-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-Phan-K%C3%ADnh-Ch%E1%BB%89/poem-Z306Hwt5c8VjxS4iOHvk6g">Đinh Sửu hạ ngũ nguyệt nhị thập vãn giai Hồ Trai Phạm tiên sinh vãng Quảng Trị phỏng Phan Kính Chỉ thi hữu tịch trung tức sự - 丁丑夏五月二十晚偕胡齋范先生往廣治訪潘敬止詩友席中即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/H%E1%BA%A1-T%E1%BB%AB-S%C6%A1n-gi%C3%A1o-th%E1%BB%A5-B%C3%B9i-th%C4%83ng-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-S%C6%A1n-tri-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-SKgkeLvjxu0CU90UKjEVeg">Hạ Từ Sơn giáo thụ Bùi thăng Đông Sơn tri huyện - 賀慈山教授裴升東山知縣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/H%E1%BA%A3o-s%E1%BB%B1-c%E1%BA%ADn/poem-DWp3Ql_JDwSkXg1eV5KIeg">Hảo sự cận - 好事近</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/author-JSRpfYAHfq-c4bVKwnYGVg">Dương Vạn Lý</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Kinh-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-th%C6%B0-x%E1%BB%A9/poem-W_wtFaebD4o1QoxiXlta5g">Kinh độc thư xứ - 經讀書處</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/K%C3%BD-c%E1%BB%AFu-D%E1%BB%8Bch-Trai-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4ng/poem-E-XnXZQNrdqMyZ9dVnhj_g">Ký cữu Dịch Trai Trần Công - 寄舅易齋陳公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://